{"tid":379141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長沙灣大廈外牆石屎剝落　擊斃地盤工人","createTime":"2017-08-29T05:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T04:52:07.000Z","uid":125959,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"877a2918882d365847253c44a94db3b8675691cd","tid":379141,"uid":125959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170829/s00001/bb07da88016264eaa3ac434a2274fa33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170829%2Fs00001%2Fbb07da88016264eaa3ac434a2274fa33.jpg&h=1d0544de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣發生大廈外牆石屎剝落擊斃地盤工人意外。<br />\n<br />\n事發早上10時許，一名68歲鋁板工人於長沙灣道650號一個地盤工作期間，旁邊的長沙灣道678號麗新商業中心5樓外牆一塊面積約3呎乘4呎的石屎突然剝落，直墜後巷。工人走避不及，被碎片擊中頭部，當場昏迷，其他工友見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場，將傷者送院搶救，最終證實不治。警方正封鎖現場，調查事故原因。"},{"pid":"ec50f01567facab49b69fe537114a916702c4705","tid":379141,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeff360fabd397d70651369bdc2498376b39d9d","tid":379141,"uid":52814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:03:46.000Z","msg":"68歲都唔退休 RIP"},{"pid":"3cdf3cf134a3e70c78aa70e26971fc4e7f553743","tid":379141,"uid":100016,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"唉，68歲仲要做"},{"pid":"7e5e24a900a45a0838cf35d692055b539bc9a7db","tid":379141,"uid":128600,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:06:01.000Z","msg":"68賠到pk"},{"pid":"d65a709612ba2b752c9fcb40a6e0c193c98f808a","tid":379141,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0488ee7e7c87b47d420091a2506c8ce36958f10d","tid":379141,"uid":85163,"like":2,"dislike":122,"score":-120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff833138021046dc337edab4ec8c95